Unicron:


Unicron flew hard left with surprising speed, avoiding the shell and three 
fire balls.  The other three fireballs struck him, doing hardly any damage 
other than scratching his frame.  He flew on, ignoring the pests, sending 
orders to the rest of the Brotherhood.
